dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Map is bordered by globes, planispheres, and diagrams of the Earth's and planetary orbits. Shows major rivers and mountains of the world. 1 map; 34 x 63 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
